{"header":"<h1>Module type <code><span>Reversible.Effectful</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Soteria_std","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Reversible","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Effectful","href":"#","kind":"module-type"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Interface for effectful reversible operations that operate on a state captured by an algebraic effect.</p><p>There is no <code>init</code> or <code>reset</code> here, initialisation and resetting is handled by <code>run</code> at the start and end of the computation.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> t</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Type of the reversible state. May be mutable!</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-backtrack_n\"><a href=\"#val-backtrack_n\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> backtrack_n : <span>int <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Remove the last <code>n</code> checkpoints.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-save\"><a href=\"#val-save\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> save : <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Save the current state as a new checkpoint.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-wrap\"><a href=\"#val-wrap\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> wrap : <span><span>(<span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Apply function <code>f</code> to the current state, may modify the state in place if it is mutable.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-run\"><a href=\"#val-run\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> run : <span><span>(<span>unit <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Runs an effectful reversible computation <code>f</code> with a fresh mutable state.</p></div></div>"}